2880 Broadway<br />
New York, NY 10025 USA
</p>



<p>
Media inquiries about research at NASA's Goddard Institute for Space Studies should be directed to the Goddard Space Flight Center <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/goddard/mediaresources/">Office of Communications</a>. Inquiries regarding Earth science research should be addressed to Peter Jacobs at that office.</p>




